{{Infobox Convention |image = [[File:Eicma logo-1.jpg|150px|Logo of the EICMA (Milan Motorcycle ) Show]] |begins = |ends = |date = Annually |location = [[FieraMilano]], [[Rho (Italy)|Rho]], [[Milan]], [[Italy]] |first = 3 May 1914 |last = 9 November 2017 – 12 November 2017 |next = 06 Nov 2018 – 11 Nov 2018 }} '''EICMA''' ('''''E'''sposizione '''I'''nternazionale '''C'''iclo '''M'''otociclo e '''A'''ccessori''), or the '''Milan Motorcycle Shows''' is an annual [[trade show]] in [[Milan, Italy]] featuring motorcycles. The 2008 show drew over half a million visitors.<ref>{{citation|url=https://www.fair-point.com/event/2016/eicma-moto/|title=EICMA 2008 facts and figures|accessdate=2009-02-25}}</ref> The show is frequently used by manufacturers to debut new models.
